%20Subhash's%20In-Laws%20React%20To%20Suicide%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20levelled%20by%20Atul%20Subhash%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%20are%20baseless%20and%20Nikita%20Singhania%2C%20his%20estranged%20wife%2C%20has%20all%20the%20answers%2C%20Nikita's%20uncle%20Sushil%20Singhania%20has%20said.%20Sushil%20Singhania%20is%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20case%20registered%20by%20Atul's%20brother%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Police%20have%20said%20they%20have%20sent%20a%20team%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Jaunpur%20to%20question%20Nikita%2C%20her%20mother%20Nisha%2C%20brother%20Anurag%20and%20uncle%20Sushil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20the%20Singhanias'%20first%20response%20to%20the%20massive%20row%20triggered%20by%20Atul%20Subhash's%20death%20by%20suicide%20and%20his%20allegations%20of%20harassment%20against%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20members%2C%2070-year-old%20Sushil%20Singhania%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20came%20to%20know%20from%20media%20reports%20that%20I%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR.%20But%20I%20have%20no%20connection%20with%20this.%20The%20(divorce)%20case%20proceedings%20have%20been%20on%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20Now%20suddenly%20this%20has%20happened.%20Our%20family%20is%20not%20guilty.%20The%20court%20will%20deliver%20its%20judgment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSubhash's%20allegations%20are%20baseless.%20Nikita%20is%20not%20here.%20Once%20she%20returns%2C%20she%20will%20respond%20to%20everything.%20She%20has%20an%20answer%20to%20every%20allegation%20they%20have%20made.%20I%20live%20separately.%20I%20am%20her%20uncle%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20have%20much%20information%20about%20the%20case.%20They%20have%20been%20handling%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20afternoon%2C%20a%20police%20team%20reached%20the%20Singhanias'%20home%20in%20Jaunpur%2C%20creating%20an%20uproar%20in%20the%20area.%20A%20police%20officer%20said%20they%20had%20just%20come%20to%20ensure%20the%20family's%20security.%20They%20denied%20any%20knowledge%20of%20Bengaluru%20police%20coming%20to%20Jaunpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20Subhash%2C%20a%2034-year-old%20techie%2C%20was%20found%20dead%20at%20his%20Bengaluru%20home%20on%20Monday%20morning.%20A%20'justice%20is%20due'%20placard%20and%20a%2024-page%20suicide%20note%20was%20found%20in%20his%20room.%20The%20note%20accused%20Nikita%20and%20her%20family%20members%20of%20harassing%20him%20during%20the%20divorce%20case%20proceedings%20to%20make%20him%20pay%20huge%20amounts%20as%20maintenance%20and%20alimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul's%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%20has%20said%20in%20his%20complaint%20to%20the%20police%20that%20Atul%20has%20detailed%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%20how%20he%20was%20being%20mentally%20and%20physically%20harassed%20and%20extorted%20by%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(DCP)%2C%20Whitefield%2C%20Shivakumar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BAtul%20Subhash%20committed%20suicide%20during%20the%20early%20hours%20of%209th%20of%20December.%20A%20complaint%20has%20been%20lodged%20at%20the%20Marathahalli%20police%20station%20in%20Bengaluru%20regarding%20this.%20Multiple%20cases%20were%20running%20against%20him%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20His%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20members%20demanded%20money%20from%20him%20to%20settle%20this%20issue%20and%20harassed%20him.%20For%20those%20reasons%2C%20he%20died%20by%20suicide.%20Based%20on%20this%20complaint%2C%20we%20registered%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20accused.%20An%20investigation%20is%20underway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%2081-minute%20video%20he%20recorded%20before%20dying%20by%20suicide%2C%20Atul%20Subhash%20said%20he%20married%20in%202019%20after%20finding%20Nikita%20on%20a%20matchmaking%20website.%20The%20couple%20had%20a%20son%20the%20next%20year.%20He%20has%20alleged%20that%20his%20wife's%20family%20would%20repeatedly%20demand%20money%20running%20into%20several%20lakhs.%20When%20he%20refused%20to%20give%20more%20money%2C%20his%20wife%20left%20the%20Bengaluru%20home%20with%20their%20son%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20the%20note%2C%20Nikita%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20him%20and%20his%20family%20under%20multiple%20sections%2C%20including%20murder%20and%20unnatural%20sex.%20She%20alleged%20that%20he%20demanded%20a%20dowry%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20and%20this%20put%20pressure%20on%20her%20father%20and%20he%20died%20of%20a%20heart%20attack.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20some%20poor%20Bollywood%20plot.%20She%20has%20already%20confessed%20that%20her%20father%20was%20suffering%20from%20long%20term%20illness%20in%20her%20cross%20examination.%20Her%20father%20was%20getting%20treated%20from%20AIIMS%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years%20for%20heart%20disease%2C%20diabetes%20etc.%20Doctors%20gave%20him%20few%20months%20and%20hence%20we%20got%20married%20quickly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20said.%20This%20case%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20subsequently%20withdrawn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20first%20demanded%20Rs%201%20crore%20to%20settle%20the%20case%2C%20but%20later%20hiked%20this%20to%20Rs%203%20crore.%20He%20has%20detailed%20a%20court%20exchange%20in%20which%20he%20said%20that%20when%20he%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20men%20are%20dying%20by%20suicide%20due%20to%20false%20cases%2C%20his%20wife%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThen%20why%20don't%20you%3F%26quot%3B%20At%20this%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20judge%20laughed%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20room.%20Atul%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20judge%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bmust%20think%20about%20his%20family%26quot%3B%20and%20demanded%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20%26quot%3Bsettle%20the%20case%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2034-year-old's%20suicide%20note%20has%20strong%20remarks%20on%20the%20justice%20system%2C%20especially%20its%20handling%20of%20marital%20disputes.%20Raging%20against%20the%20law%20dealing%20with%20such%20cases%2C%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20his%20suicide%20note%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20I%20work%20hard%20and%20become%20better%20at%20my%20work%2C%20the%20more%20I%20and%20my%20family%20will%20be%20harassed%20and%20extorted%20and%20the%20whole%20legal%20system%20will%20encourage%20and%20help%20my%20harassers...%20Now%2C%20with%20me%20gone%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20money%20and%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20reason%20to%20harass%20my%20old%20parents%20and%20my%20brother.%20I%20may%20have%20destroyed%20my%20body%20but%20it%20has%20saved%20everything%20I%20believe%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733918880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fobhvpcu8_atul-subhash-nikita-uncle-split_625x300_11_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fatul-subhashs-wife-has-all-the-answers-in-laws-1st-reaction-to-suicide-7223590%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAtul%20Subhash's%20Wife%20Has%20All%20The%20Answers%26quot%3B%3A%20In-Laws'%201st%20Reaction%20To%20Suicide%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUr