he%20four%20serving%20and%20former%20military%20and%20security%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named%20due%20to%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20large%20phenomenon%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shalom%20Ben%20Hanan%2C%20a%20former%20top%20Shin%20Bet%20official%2C%20referring%20to%20what%20he%20called%20the%20surprising%20number%20of%20Jewish%20citizens%20who%20knowingly%20agreed%20to%20work%20for%20Iran%20against%20the%20state%20with%20intelligence%20gathering%20or%20planning%20sabotage%20and%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShin%20Bet%20and%20the%20police%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Iran's%20foreign%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20media%20after%20the%20wave%20of%20arrests%2C%20Iran's%20U.N.%20mission%20did%20not%20confirm%20or%20deny%20seeking%20to%20recruit%20Israelis%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20a%20logical%20standpoint%26quot%3B%20any%20such%20efforts%20by%20Iranian%20intelligence%20services%20would%20focus%20on%20non-Iranian%20and%20non-Muslim%20individuals%20to%20lessen%20suspicion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20two%20suspects%20were%20from%20Israel's%20ultra-Orthodox%20community%2C%20police%20and%20the%20Shin%20Bet%20have%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Iranian%20espionage%20operations%20in%20previous%20decades%20that%20recruited%20a%20high-profile%20businessman%20and%20a%20former%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20the%20new%20alleged%20spies%20were%20largely%20people%20on%20the%20fringes%20of%20Israeli%20society%2C%20including%20recent%20immigrants%2C%20an%20army%20deserter%20and%20a%20convicted%20sex%20offender%2C%20conversations%20with%20the%20sources%2C%20court%20records%20and%20official%20statements%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20their%20activity%20was%20limited%20to%20spraying%20anti-Netanyahu%20or%20anti-government%20graffiti%20on%20walls%20and%20damaging%20cars%2C%20Shin%20Bet%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20arrests%20and%20involvement%20of%20so%20many%20Jewish%20Israelis%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Arab%20citizens%2C%20has%20caused%20concern%20in%20Israel%20at%20a%20time%20it%20remains%20at%20war%20with%20Iran-backed%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20deal%20with%20Hezbollah%20remains%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShin%20Bet%20on%20Oct.%2021%20said%20the%20espionage%20activities%20were%20%26quot%3Bamong%20the%20most%20severe%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20has%20known.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20arrests%20also%20follow%20a%20wave%20of%20attempted%20hits%20and%20kidnappings%20linked%20to%20Tehran%20in%20Europe%20and%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unusual%20decision%20to%20provide%20detailed%20public%20accounts%20of%20the%20alleged%20plots%20was%20a%20move%20by%20Israel's%20security%20services%20to%20signal%20both%20to%20Iran%20and%20potential%20saboteurs%20inside%20Israel%20that%20they%20would%20be%20caught%2C%20Ben%20Hanan%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20want%20to%20alert%20the%20public.%20And%20you%20also%20want%20to%20make%20an%20example%20of%20people%20that%20may%20also%20have%20intentions%20or%20plans%20to%20co-operate%20with%20the%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20achieved%20major%20intelligence%20successes%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20in%20a%20shadow%20war%20with%20its%20regional%20foe%2C%20including%20allegedly%20killing%20a%20top%20nuclear%20scientist.%20With%20the%20recent%20arrests%20Israel%20has%20%26quot%3Bso%20far%26quot%3B%20thwarted%20Tehran's%20efforts%20to%20respond%2C%20one%20active%20military%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20been%20weakened%20by%20Israel's%20attacks%20on%20its%20proxy%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20the%20related%20fall%20of%20Tehran's%20ally%2C%20former%20president%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESOCIAL%20MEDIA%20RECRUITS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20intelligence%20agencies%20often%20find%20potential%20recruits%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20Israeli%20police%20said%20in%20a%20video%20released%20in%20November%20warning%20of%20ongoing%20infiltration%20attempts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recruiting%20efforts%20are%20at%20times%20direct.%20One%20message%20sent%20to%20an%20Israeli%20civilian%20and%20seen%20by%20Reuters%20promised%20%2415%2C000%20in%20exchange%20for%20information%2C%20with%20an%20email%20and%20number%20to%20call.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20also%20approached%20expatriate%20networks%20of%20Jews%20from%20Caucasus%20countries%20living%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20United%20States%2C%20said%20one%20of%20the%20sources%2C%20a%20former%20senior%20official%20who%20worked%20on%20Israel's%20counter%20espionage%20efforts%20until%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20authorities%20have%20said%20publicly%20some%20of%20the%20Jewish%20suspects%20were%20originally%20from%20Caucasus%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecruited%20individuals%20are%20first%20assigned%20innocuous-seeming%20tasks%20in%20return%20for%20money%2C%20before%20handlers%20gradually%20demand%20specific%20intelligence%20on%20targets%2C%20including%20about%20individuals%20and%20sensitive%20military%20infrastructure%2C%20backed%20by%20the%20threat%20of%20blackmail%2C%20said%20the%20former%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20Israeli%20suspect%2C%20Vladislav%20Victorsson%2C%2030%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20Oct.%2014%20along%20with%20his%2018-year-old%20girlfriend%20in%20the%20Israeli%20city%20of%20Ramat%20Gan%20near%20Tel%20Aviv.%20He%20had%20been%20jailed%20in%202015%20for%20sex%20with%20minors%20as%20young%20as%2014%2C%20according%20to%20a%20court%20indictment%20from%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20acquaintance%20of%20Victorsson%20told%20Reuters%20he%20had%20told%20her%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20Iranians%20usi