ee%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEmployees%20may%20feel%20disempowered%2C%20undervalued%2C%20and%20overly%20scrutinized%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhich%20stifles%20creativity%20and%20collaboration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrue%20effective%20leadership%2C%20Holliday-Quinn%20said%2C%20requires%20%26quot%3Bresilience%2C%20self-awareness%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20trust%2C%20collaboration%2C%20and%20empowerment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20leaders%20who%20leave%20a%20lasting%20legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNot%20just%20in%20terms%20of%20success%20but%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20positive%20impact%20they%20have%20on%20their%20organizations%20and%20the%20people%20within%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeck%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frocket-lab-ceo-beck-paranoia-superpower-can-lead-to-burnout-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733912131000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67582e4452dd0818d1a62821%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frocket-lab-ceo-beck-paranoia-superpower-can-lead-to-burnout-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rocket%20Lab's%20Peter%20Beck%20views%20paranoia%20as%20a%20leadership%20asset%20but%20experts%20caution%20about%20burnout%20risks%2C%20urging%20balance%20in%20high-pressure%20environments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ldodgson%40businessinsider.com%20(Lindsay%20Dodgson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frocket-lab-ceo-beck-paranoia-superpower-can-lead-to-burnout-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tech%20recap%202024%3A%20Top%205%20mid-range%20smartphones%20from%20OnePlus%2C%20M