A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm64glt6_rajya-sabha-pti_625x300_06_December_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20rare%20development%20has%20marred%20the%20functioning%20of%20Parliament%20in%20its%20seven-decade%20history.%20The%20collective%20decision%20by%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20to%20submit%20a%20motion%20against%20the%20Chairman%20on%20Tuesday%20is%20unprecedented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20move%2C%20despite%20the%20Opposition's%20lack%20of%20bench%20strength%20and%20awareness%20of%20the%20technical%20shortcomings%2C%20highlights%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20relations%20have%20soured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20motion%20against%20Chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankhar%20was%20thought%20of%20during%20the%20previous%20session%20and%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%20ongoing%20winter%20session%2C%20driven%20by%20charges%20of%20his%20partisan%20conduct.%20The%20Opposition%20pressed%20ahead%20with%20the%20motion%20even%20though%20it%20fell%20short%20of%20the%20mandatory%2014-day%20notice%20required%20for%20such%20a%20motion%20to%20be%20brought%20before%20the%20House%20for%20consideration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Never-Ending%20Saga%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20standoff%20between%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20has%20become%20a%20regular%20phenomenon%20in%20Parliament%2C%20as%20have%20the%20disruptions%20and%20turbulence.%20However%2C%20severe%20disagreement%20regarding%20the%20functioning%20or%20conduct%20of%20the%20Chair%20has%20not%20been%20raised%20in%20this%20manner%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20until%20now.%20Parliamentary%20managers%20from%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20and%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20spokespersons%20have%20engaged%20with%20the%20Opposition%2C%20providing%20reasons%20behind%20their%20actions.%20Yet%2C%20what%20remains%20unspoken%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20entire%20Opposition%E2%80%94heterogeneous%20and%20with%20separate%20priorities%E2%80%94has%20made%20common%20cause.%20This%20unified%20step%20should%20be%20evaluated%20dispassionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Opposition%20signalled%20its%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Upper%20House%20by%20submitting%20a%20similar%20motion%20against%20the%20Deputy%20Chairman.%20That%20motion%20was%20also%20rejected%20as%20it%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20mandated%20notice%20period%20requirements.%20Nevertheless%2C%20this%20development%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20symptomatic%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20perception%20of%20being%20denied%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20presiding%20officers%20is%20rare%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20where%20motions%20were%20submitted%20against%20Speakers%20G.V.%20Mavalankar%20(1954)%2C%20Hukum%20Singh%20(1966)%2C%20and%20Balram%20Jakhar%20(1987).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20And%20Its%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliament%20consists%20of%20both%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20members%20and%20the%20Opposition.%20In%20the%20era%20of%20coalitions%2C%20another%20phenomenon%20has%20emerged.%20Some%20parties%20occupy%20a%20middle%20ground%2C%20often%20characterised%20as%20maintaining%20an%20%E2%80%9Cequidistant%E2%80%9D%20position%20from%20either%20side%20and%20offering%2C%20at%20best%2C%20%E2%80%9Cissue-based%E2%80%9D%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20a%20party%20with%20a%20majority%2C%20whether%20on%20its%20own%20or%20in%20coalition%2C%20is%20comfortable%20with%20its%20bench%20strength%2C%20the%20situation%20changes.%20It%20is%20here%20that%20parliamentary%20managers%20on%20all%20sides%20play%20a%20crucial%20role.%20These%20leaders%20often%20meet%20across%20the%20table%20to%20resolve%20differences%20and%20find%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20discussion%20took%20place%20as%20recently%20as%2010%20days%20ago.%20The%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition%20came%20to%20an%20understanding%2C%20with%20the%20government%20agreeing%20to%20hold%20a%20debate%20on%20the%20Constitution%20in%20both%20Houses%2C%20while%20the%20Opposition%20suspended%20its%20agitational%20approach.%20However%2C%20this%20truce%20now%20seems%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20sufficient%20parliamentary%20devices%20in%20the%20rule%20book%20for%20the%20Opposition%20to%20raise%20concerns%2C%20the%20main%20issue%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20priority%20and%20specific%20provisions%20being%20invoked.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20Opposition%20attempts%20to%20raise%20an%20issue%20through%20an%20Adjournment%20Motion%2C%20while%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Rule%20267%20is%20invoked.%20The%20decision%20to%20admit%20or%20reject%20these%20motions%20rests%20with%20the%20Chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20such%20stand-offs%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition%20were%20resolved%20through%20a%20collective%20approach%2C%20with%20both%20sides%20finding%20a%20midpoint%20between%20their%20maximalist%20positions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20There%20A%20Solution%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParliamentary%20managers%2C%20particularly%20on%20the%20ruling%20side%2C%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20ensuring%20that%20the%20businesses%20of%20the%20Houses%20are%20conducted%20and%20that%20the%20legislative%20agenda%20moves%20forward.%20The%20Opposition%20must%20understand%20that%20stalling%20Parliament%20cannot%20continue%20indefinitely.%20While%20creating%20pressure%20on%20the%20government%20is%20one%20aspect%2C%20interrupting%20parliamentary%20work%20creates%20a%20perception%20that%20the%20institution%20is%20dysfunctional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisruptions%20and%20the%20stalling%20of%20proceedings%20in%20both%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20have%20been%20a%20recurring%20phenomenon%20since%20the%20mid-1980s.%20Despite%20several%20attempts%20and%20resolutions%20adopted%20by%20leaders%20on%20many%20occasions%2C%20such%20as%20on%20Parliament's%2050th%20anniversary%2C%20to%20avoid%20these%20practices%2C%20they%20have%20become%20entrenched%2C%20irrespective%20of%20which%20party%20is%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20potential%20solution%20could%20be%20to%20adopt%20the%20practice%20of%20designating%20specific%20days%20for%20the%20Opposition%2C%20as%20done%20in%20the%20British%20and%20Canadian%20Parliaments.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20adage%20holds%20that%20while%20the%20opposition%20can%20have%20its%20say%2C%20the%20government%20must%20have%20its%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(K.V.%20Prasad%20is%20a%20senior%20Delhi-based%20journalist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733911920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fm64glt6_rajya-sabha-pti_625x300_06_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-opposition-vs-centre-a-battle-that-keeps-worsening-7223526%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lack%20of%20trust%20in%20presiding%20officers%20is%20rare%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20instances%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20where%20motions%20were%20submitted%20against%20Speakers%20G.V.%20Mavalankar%20(1954)%2C%20Hukum%20Singh%20(1966)%2C%20and%20Balram%20Jakhar%20(1987).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fopinion-opposition-vs-centre-a-battle-that-keeps-worsening-7223526%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blackpink%20Member%20Jisoo%20and%20Park%20Jeong-min%E2%80%99s%20Korean%20Zombie%20Series%20%E2%80%98Newtopia%E2%80%99%20Sets%20Prime%20Video%20Release%20Date%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733911623000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2