0on%20average%20as%20other%20posts%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20concept%20of%20LinkedIn%20video%20might%20feel%20strange%20to%20some%20users%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20key%20for%20the%20platform%20to%20cement%20itself%20as%20a%20core%20platform%20for%20creators%2C%20unlock%20more%20ad%20revenue%2C%C2%A0and%20keep%20people%20checking%20their%20feeds%20regularly.%20The%20top%20platforms%20for%20creators%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20TikTok%2C%20and%20Instagram%2C%20are%20all%20heavily%20focused%20on%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20on%20a%20personal%20mission%20to%20make%20LinkedIn%20a%20daily%20habit%20for%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Jam%C3%A9%20Jackson%2C%20a%20LinkedIn%20community%20manager%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20so%20much%20more%20than%20just%20a%20platform%20for%20job%20searching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20LinkedIn's%20first%20attempt%20at%20video.%20In%202019%2C%20LinkedIn%20launched%20its%20live%20video%20product.%20In%202020%2C%20it%20launched%20a%20%26quot%3BStories%26quot%3B%20feature%2C%20which%20lets%20users%20share%20disappearing%20videos%20(that%20shut%20down%20in%202021).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20there%20is%20some%20indication%20that%20this%20current%2C%20TikTok-like%20push%20might%20be%20what%20finally%20breaks%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20investments%20in%20rich%20formats%2C%20like%20video%2C%20strengthen%20our%20leadership%20in%20B2B%20advertising%20and%20amplify%20the%20value%20we%20deliver%20to%20our%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-ceo-satya-nadella-career-rise%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Satya%20Nadella%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20October%20earnings%20call.%20%26quot%3BWeekly%20immersive%20video%20views%20increased%206x%20quarter-over-quarter%20and%20total%20video%20viewership%20on%20LinkedIn%20is%20up%2036%25%20year-over-year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224f8f9fd3-3230-4aef-a7c1-41044a0ba3a3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELinkedIn's%20do's%20and%20don'ts%20for%20video%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20makes%20a%20good%20LinkedIn%20video%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJackson%20said%20to%20avoid%20creating%20content%20that%20%26quot%3Bfeels%20way%20too%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Esales-y%20and%20promotional%26quot%3B%20and%20to%20keep%20the%20video%20to%20under%20two%20minutes%3A%20short%2C%20snappy%2C%20and%20actionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20call%20to%20action%20is%20important%20because%20I%20always%20like%20to%20secretly%20tell%20people%20that%20the%20comments%20section%20is%20the%20liquid%20gold%20of%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20you%20do%20that%20is%20by%20inviting%20people%20to%20the%20party%2C%20inviting%20them%20to%20the%20table%20after%20you've%20created%20that%20video%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20share%20in%20the%20comments%20things%20that%20they%20have%20learned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20has%20also%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20%26quot%3Bfaceless%20video%20content%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20people%20aren't%20front%20and%20center%2C%20Jackson%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20had%20generally%20performed%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20has%20encouraged%20CEOs%20and%20executives%20to%20talk%20about%20breaking%20news%20as%20well%2C%20Jackson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22224326a3-bbaf-4398-84b1-320a77889e79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreators%20are%20using%20video%20to%20grow%20audiences%20but%20monetization%20lags%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECreators%20generally%20say%20that%20compared%20to%20other%20platforms%20like%20TikTok%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20LinkedIn%20is%20much%20less%20saturated%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20an%20opportunity%20to%20build%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20posting%20on%20LinkedIn%20almost%20daily%2C%20certainly%20every%20weekday%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Avi%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20has%2023%2C000%20LinkedIn%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGandhi%20has%20recently%20focused%20on%20short-form%20video%20content%2C%20posting%20three%20to%20four%20times%20a%20week%20and%20often%20promoting%20his%20newsletter%20by%20calling%20out%20the%20name%20and%20including%20a%20link%20to%20subscribe%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20text%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECareer%20coach%20and%20creator%20Jahleane%20Dolne%20said%20she%20often%20uses%20LinkedIn%20to%20post%20podcast%20clips.%20While%20her%20largest%20following%20is%20on%20TikTok%20(about%2034%2C000)%2C%20Dolne%20said%20her%20podcast%20clips%20are%20a%20better%20fit%20for%20the%20LinkedIn%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20audience%20growth%20for%20some%20creators%2C%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-ways-to-make-money-as-content-creator%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20LinkedIn%20isn't%20yet%20fully%20developed.%20That%20may%20be%20changing%2C%20though.%20Three%20of%20the%20creators%20BI%20spoke%20with%20said%20they%20were%20either%20already%20working%20on%20LinkedIn-focused%20brand%20deals%20or%20actively%20reaching%20out%20to%20potential%20sponsors.%20And%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20marketing%20agency%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tubefilter.com%2F2024%2F03%2F05%2Flinkedin-influencer-marketing-company-creator-authority-agency-brendan-gahan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECreator%20Authority%3C%2Fa%3E%20launched%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20platform%20has%20not%20yet%20introduced%20a%20monetization%20program%20similar%20to%20those%20on%20Instagram%2C%20TikTok%2C%20or%20YouTube%20that%20directly%20pays%20creators.%3C%