20don't%20even%20remember%20your%20face%20now%20till%20I%20see%20pictures%20of%20you%20when%20you%20were%201%20year%20old.%20I%20don't%20feel%20anything%20about%20you%20now%20except%20a%20tinge%20of%20pain%20sometimes.%20Now%2C%20You%20just%20feel%20like%20a%20blackmail%20using%20which%20I%20will%20be%20extorted%20more%20and%20more.%20Though%20it%20would%20hurt%20you%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20now%20you%20feel%20like%20a%20mistake%20I%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20Atul%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter%20in%20which%20he%20detailed%20how%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20family%20were%20allegedly%20using%20his%20son%20to%20extort%20money%20from%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20said%20that%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20pay%20his%20wife%20a%20maintenance%20of%20Rs%2080%2C000%20per%20month%20for%20herself%20and%20their%20son%2C%20but%20Nikita%20wanted%20this%20to%20be%20increased%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20just%20sad%20that%20this%20shameless%20system%20can%20make%20a%20child%20a%20burden%20and%20liability%20to%20his%20father.%20I%20have%20met%20a%20lot%20of%20alienated%20fathers%2C%20most%20of%20them%20speak%20of%20similar%20feelings%20when%20they%20are%20being%20honest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtul%20has%20said%20that%20his%20wife%20did%20not%20let%20him%20meet%20his%20son%20since%20they%20separated%20in%202021.%20His%20brother%20Bikas%20Kumar%20has%20said%20in%20his%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20complaint%20that%20Nikita%20had%20demanded%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20from%20Atul%20to%20let%20him%20meet%20their%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTill%20I%20am%20alive%20and%20make%20money%2C%20they%20will%20use%20you%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20harass%20your%20grandparents%2C%20uncle%20and%20me%20to%20extort%20more%20and%20more%20money%20from%20me.%20I%20can't%20let%20all%20this%20harass%20my%20father%2C%20mother%20and%20brother%20unnecessarily.%20Not%20even%20for%20you.%C2%A0I%20can%20sacrifice%20100%20sons%20like%20you%20for%20my%20father.%20I%20can%20sacrifice