nths%20of%20cutting%20expenses%20and%20tracking%20every%20dollar%20to%20pay%20off%20my%20debt.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20finance%20officer%2C%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20to%20open%20up%20about%20my%20money%20mistakes%2C%20but%20I%20started%20sharing%20my%20story%20with%20people%20in%20my%20circle.%20Encouraged%20by%20their%20positive%20responses%2C%20I%20posted%20about%20it%20on%20social%20media%20and%20built%20a%20following.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20there%20was%20a%20need%20for%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffintech-startup-female-invest-raises-equity-plots-us-growth-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebetter%20financial%20education%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%20for%20women.%20I%20wanted%20to%20use%20my%20expertise%20to%20help%20others%20and%20build%20a%20flexible%20business%20but%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20start.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20first%20encountered%20online%20business%20coaches%20through%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-financial-literacy-tools-build-wealth-bl2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblogs%20and%20podcasts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20digital%20entrepreneurs.%20I%20found%20a%20coach%20who%20positioned%20themself%20as%20an%20expert%20in%20building%20profitable%20businesses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20coach%20offered%20a%20free%20three-day%20online%20workshop%20on%20how%20to%20create%20a%20compelling%20brand%20story.%20The%20workshop%20featured%20many%20of%20their%20affiliates%20%E2%80%94%20people%20I%20was%20familiar%20with%20from%20my%20research%20%E2%80%94%20and%20past%20students.%20After%20the%20event%2C%20the%20coach%20pitched%20a%20paid%20course%20on%20building%20your%20business%20around%20a%20strong%20brand%20message.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20found%20the%20free%20workshop%20very%20helpful%20and%20thought%20their%20course%20would%20help%20me%20clarify%20my%20story%20and%20sign%20clients.%20The%20initial%20course%20cost%20around%20%241%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20course%2C%20I%20still%20didn't%20feel%20confident%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-become-successful-entrepreneur-according-to-career-coach-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estarting%20a%20business%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20coach%20pitched%20one-on-one%20coaching%20program%2C%20a%20five-figure%20investment.%20I%20hesitated%20but%20thought%20this%20was%20the%20push%20I%20needed%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c15fd9f7-d76f-4db4-816f-10659c4eabe9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20coaching%20promised%20vs.%20what%20it%20delivered%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20just%20finished%20paying%20off%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-coach-explains-how-she-paid-off-credit-card-debt-2024-10%3Finternational%3Dtrue%26r%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecredit%20card%20debt%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20was%20working%20full-time%20as%20a%20finance%20officer%20while%20building%20my%20business%20on%20the%20side.%20I%20didn't%20have%20savings%20to%20pay%20for%20coaching%2C%20so%20I%20used%20a%20combination%20of%20my%20credit%20card%20and%20monthly%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20researched%20other%20coaches%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20another%20general%20course.%20I'd%20already%20invested%20in%20this%20coach's%20course%2C%20so%20it%20like%20a%20logical%20next%20step.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20coaching%20program%20was%20an%20hourlong%201%3A1%20session%20once%20a%20week%20over%20seven%20weeks.%20The%20program%20would%20help%20me%20refine%20my%20story%2C%20create%20a%20business%20strategy%2C%20and%20start%20generating%20revenue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20sessions%20felt%20unstructured.%20Each%20week%2C%20I%20would%20discuss%20my%20progress%20and%20ask%20for%20guidance%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20overarching%20plan.%20The%20focus%20was%20on%20reviewing%20if%20I'd%20completed%20what%20we%20discussed%20in%20the%20previous%20session.%20Often%2C%20my%20coach%20would%20repeat%20similar%20concepts%20rather%20than%20introduce%20new%20strategies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230aa8d6b-793b-4159-aa2d-dbf78dba4a87%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20investment%20was%20not%20worth%20it%20to%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20the%20third%20session%2C%20I%20expressed%20my%20frustration%20with%20not%20progressing%20and%20feeling%20overwhelmed.%20In%20between%20meetings%2C%20I%20mentioned%20that%20some%20of%20the%20advice%2C%20like%20sharing%20personal%20stories%20that%20didn't%20feel%20connected%20to%20my%20business%2C%20felt%20irrelevant.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20day%2C%20I%20told%20the%20coach%20outright%20that%20I%20preferred%20to%20spend%20time%20talking%20to%20people%20about%20their%20struggles%20instead%20of%20sharing%20my%20own%20stories.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20the%20coach%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20it's%20not%20working%20because%20you're%20too%20messy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPart%20of%20this%20comment%20stemmed%20from%20my%20choice%20to%20skip%20some%20of%20the%20resources%20they%20had%20provided%2C%20like%20a%20sales%20tracking%20spreadsheet%20and%20a%20guide%20on%20how%20to%20win%20sales%20calls%20(because%20I%20wasn't%20making%20those%20calls%20yet).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20also%20partly%20about%20me%20wanting%20to%20move%20ahead%20with%20multiple%20areas%20of%20my%20business%20instead%20of%20focusing%20on%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20comment%20hit%20hard.%20I'd%20always%20been%20OK%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fend-remote-work-could-hurt-overemployed-workers-job-jugglers-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ejuggling%20multiple%20projects%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20for%20months%20after%20that%20session%2C%20I%20doubted%20myself.%20I%20believed%20that%20my%20%26quot%3Bmessiness%26quot%3B%20was%20holding%20me%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20agreement%2C%20I%20couldn't%20cancel%20or%20request%20a%20refund%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20keep%20paying%20for%20the%20coaching%20program%20even%20though%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20invested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20stopped%20working%20on%20my%20business%20for%20a%20while%20and%20focused%20instead%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-workers-shocked-by-nine-to-five-work-schedule-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emy%209-to-5%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20final%20payment%20went%20through%2C%20I%20felt%20frustrated%20I%20had%20spent%20so%20much%20money%20and%20relieved%20that%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20revisit%20the%20tools%20and%20resources%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20finishing%20my%20coaching%20sessions%2C%20I%20ditched%20the%20spreadsheets%20and%20went%20back%20to%20experimenting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20followed%20my%20instincts%20and%20launched%20my%20business%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbrownwaytomoney.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Brown%20Way%20to%20Money%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Now%2C%20I%20run%20a%20platform%20that%20offers%20money%20management%2C%20financial%20literacy%20support%20and%20financial%20education%20dedicated%20to%20women%20entrepreneurs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20became%20pregnant%20I%20had%20to%20delegate%20tasks%20to%20what%20is%20now%20my%20team.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20realized%20that%20my%20%26quot%3Bmessy%26quot%3B%20approach%20was%20actually%20my%20strength.%20%3Cspan%3EPeople%20commented%20on%20how%20surprising%20it%20was%20that%20I%20could%20juggle%20so%20much.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22924b946f-f250-4d31-a980-1eecdd88d7f9%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20considered%20before%20investing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don't%20see%20my%20first%20coaching%20experience%20as%20a%20complete%20failure.%20It%20taught%20me%20that%20I%20am%20ultimately%20responsible%20for%20every%20business%20decision.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20worked%20with%20coaches%20who%20have%20significantly%20contributed%20to%20my%20growth%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%2C%20but%20it%20took%20years%20before%20I%20felt%20ready%20to%20invest%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20that%20point%2C%20I%20had%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20my%20goals%20and%20what%20stage%20I%20was%20at%20with%20my%20business.%20This%20made%20it%20easier%20to%20hire%20a%20coach%20to%20help%20me%20build%20specific%20skills%20I%20couldn't%20develop%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere's%20what%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20considered%20earlier%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EClearly%20defining%20my%20goals%20and%20desired%20outcomes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20I%20now%20take%20the%20time%20to%20outline%20what%20I%20want%20to%20achieve%20with%20a%20coach.%20I%20discuss%20my%20goals%20with%20the%20potential%20coach%20beforehand%20to%20ensure%20we're%20aligned%20and%20have%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20reaching%20those%20outcomes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EResearching%20the%20coach's%20expertise%20and%20relevance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Now%2C%20I%20look%20into%20their%20social%20media%2C%20reviews%20and%2C%20when%20possible%2C%20speak%20with%20past%20clients%20to%20understand%20their%20approach.%20Their%20expertise%20needs%20to%20align%20specifically%20with%20the%20stage%20of%20my%20business%20and%20my%20goals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdopting%20a%20return-on-investment%20mindset%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EInstead%20of%20assuming%20the%20coaching%20experience%20will%20%26quot%3Bwork%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20own%2C%20I%20focus%20on%20how%20I%20can%20capitalize%20on%20the%20skills%20and%20knowledge%20I'll%20gain.%20I%20evaluate%20whether%20the%20potential%20ROI%20is%20clear%20and%20sufficient%20before%20committing.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-self-doubt-tips-finding-right-fit-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733910152000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67214b76a0a0cc14f224ca82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-self-doubt-tips-finding-right-fit-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Alejandra%20Roja%20spend%20over%20%2410%2C000%20on%20a%20business%20coach%20who%20was%20a%20bad%20fit%20for%20Roja's%20needs%20when%20she%20was%20just%20starting%20her%20journey%20as%20an%20entrepreneur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Alejandra%20Rojas)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-coach-self-doubt-tips-finding-right-fit-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TMC's%20Kalyan%20Banerjee%20slams%20BJP%2C%20Congress%20for%20disrupting%20Parliament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733909777000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116208856%2Cimgsize-40792.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2