vil%20law%20at%20Idlib%20University.%20Before%20entering%20politics%2C%20he%20worked%20for%20Syria's%20state%20gas%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMohammad%20al-Bashir%20was%20the%20head%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CSalvation%20Government%20(SG)%2C%E2%80%9D%20established%20in%20Idlib%20in%202017%20to%20manage%20governance%20in%20the%20rebel-held%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Salvation%20Government%20operated%20like%20a%20state%2C%20with%20ministries%2C%20judicial%20authorities%2C%20and%20a%20religious%20council%20based%20on%20Islamic%20law.%20Under%20Mr%20Bashir's%C2%A0leadership%2C%20the%20SG%20took%20over%20public%20services%20in%20Aleppo%20after%C2%A0HTS%20and%20allies%20took%20over%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20restoring%20electricity%2C%20telecommunications%2C%20and%20other%20essential%20services.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBefore%20leading%20the%20government%2C%20he%20held%20the%20role%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20minister%E2%80%9D%20within%20the%20same%20administration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20is%20Assad%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESyrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%2C%20who%20fled%20to%20Moscow%2C%20was%20ousted%20after%20rebel%20forces%2C%20spearheaded%20by%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%2C%20took%20control%20of%20Damascus.%20Jolani%20vowed%20to%20pursue%20those%20responsible%20for%20war%20crimes%20and%20torture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Assad%20regime%2C%20families%20of%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20missing%20detainees%20have%20mobilised%2C%20searching%20for%20their%20loved%20ones%20held%20in%20prisons.%20As%20rebels%20advanced%2C%20they%20released%20many%20prisoners%20but%20many%20more%20remain%20unaccounted%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20has%20said%20that%20whoever%20emerges%20in%20power%20must%20hold%20Assad%20and%20his%20associates%20accountable%20for%20their%20crimes.%20Syrian%20rescue%20groups%20are%20calling%20for%20assistance%20in%20locating%20secret%2