3Cp%3EIn%20a%20historic%20first%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20on%20Tuesday%20moved%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fno-confidence-motion%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fjagdeep-dhankhar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJagdeep%20Dhankhar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alleging%20partisan%20functioning%20of%20the%20House%20under%20his%20stewardship.%20The%20notice%20was%20tabled%20this%20morning%2C%20triggering%20the%20inevitable%20squabbling%20and%20an%20adjournment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20of%20the%20motion%20followed%20a%20raucous%2048%20hours%20in%20Parliament%3B%20the%20Upper%20and%20Lower%20House%20both%20saw%20chaos%20and%20disruptions%20as%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%20clashed%20over%20the%20ruling%20party's%20allegations%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsonia-gandhi-linked-to-organisation-financed-by-george-soros-foundation-bjp-7200687%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20Congress%20MP%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20businessman%20George%20Soros%20are%20colluding%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20defame%20India%2C%20adversely%20impact%20its%20economy%2C%20and%20harm%20national%20security%2C%20a%20charge%20the%20party%20firmly%20rubbished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20last%20count%2060%20opposition%20MPs%20-%20including%20those%20from%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%2C%20and%20the%20AAP%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20parties%20that%20often%20disagree%20with%20the%20Congress%20-%20had%20backed%20the%20move%2C%20which%20is%20a%20first%20in%20Indian%20parliamentary%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20motion%20was%20submitted%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1944038%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArticle%2067(B)%20of%20the%20Constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20Vice%20President.%20But%20since%20the%20VEEP%20-%20also%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20-%20is%20also%20the%20ex%20officio%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chair%2C%20removing%20one%20removes%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20Article%2067(B)%20Say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20a%20Vice-President%20may%20be%20removed%20from%20his%20office%20by%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20Council%20of%20States%20passed%20by%20a%20majority%20of%20all%20the%20then%20members%20of%20the%20Council%20and%20agreed%20to%20by%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%3B%20but%20no%20resolution%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20this%20clause%20shall%20be%20moved%20unless%20at%20least%20fourteen%20days'%20notice%20has%20been%20given%20of%20the%20intention%20to%20move%20the%20resolution...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20potential%20stumbling%20block%20for%20the%20opposition%20is%20the%2014-day%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20opposition%20is%20compelled%20to%20submit%20a%2014-day%20notice%2C%20then%20it%20means%20the%20motion%20cannot%20be%20debated%20this%20session%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20to%20finish%20on%20December%2020%20-%20nine%20days%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20is%20aware%20of%20this%2C%20and%20the%20improbability%20of%20their%20motion%20being%20carried%2C%20but%20have%20insisted%20this%20is%20not%20about%20the%20numbers%2C%20that%20it%20is%20about%20sending%20a%20message%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20symbolic%20move%2C%20sources%20within%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20have%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20Numbers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20motion%20is%20somehow%20allowed%20to%20be%20voted%20on%2C%20in%20politics%20it%20comes%20down%2C%20always%2C%20to%20the%20numbers.%20And%20does%20the%20opposition%20have%20the%20numbers%20to%20carry%20its%20motion%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nutshell%2C%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2067(B)%20requires%20a%20simple%20majority%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20-%20i.e.%2C%20half%20of%20those%20voting%20%2B%201%20-%20for%20it%20to%20be%20passed.%20As%20of%20today%2C%20that%20number%20is%20116%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20at%20full%20strength%2C%20has%20245%20members%20but%2014%20seats%20are%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20for%20now%2C%20has%20significantly%20fewer%20than%20116%20MPs%20on%20its%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20could%20increase%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20the%20BJP-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20is%20in%20control.%20As%20of%20September%2C%20it%20has%20a%20six-seat%20majority%2C%20not%20counting%20fence-sitters%20like%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnda-touches-majority-mark-in-rajya-sabha-after-12-members-elected-unopposed-6429838%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E12%20MPs%20Elected%20Unopposed%20To%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20NDA%20At%20Majority%20Mark%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20including%20those%20not%20with%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20have%20only%2085%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20move%20that%20goalpost%2C%20called%20out%20the%20YSRCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWill%20Jagan%20party%20have%20the%20courage%20to%20support%20the%20opposition's%20motion%20on%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20issue%2C%20or%20will%20he%20stay%20loyal%20to%20Modi%20and%20Shah%20while%20making%20empty%20statements%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDhankar%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Dhankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FRajyaSabha%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23RajyaSabha%3C%2Fa%3E%20%