lace%20of%20the%20butter%20chicken%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmotimahal.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoti%20Mahal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Chef%20Davinder%20Kumar%2C%20executive%20chef%2C%20Hotel%20Le%20Meridien%2C%20Delhi%2C%20it%20is%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20restaurant%20that%20draws%20him%20to%20it.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20very%20few%20restaurants%20that%20maintain%20the%20recipe%2C%20the%20taste%20and%20the%20aroma.%20With%20butter%20chicken%2C%20the%20skill%20lies%20in%20creating%20the%20aroma%3B%20when%20you%20keep%20adding%20elements%20to%20the%20dish%20it%20loses%20its%20personality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChef%20Vikas%20Vibhuti%2C%20agrees.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20memories%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346520%2Flist-of-iconic-food-places-peter-cat-tunday-kababi-paragon-amrik-sukhdev-mtr-karims-ram-ashraya%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20iconic%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20associated%20with%20my%20OCLD%20(The%20Oberoi%20Centre%20of%20Learning%20and%20Development)%20days.%20It%20was%20a%20ritual%20every%20weekend%20to%20visit%20and%20enjoy%20butter%20chicken%20with%20%3Cem%3Echilli%20%3C%2Fem%3Egarlic%20%3Cem%3Enaan%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20flatbread).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Mughal%20Mahal%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWriter%20Marryam%20H%20Reshii%20calls%20the%20eatery%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20big%20daddy%20of%20butter%20chicken%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CCompetitors%20live%20in%20hope%20of%20uncovering%20some%20secret%20stash%20of%20canned%20Pelati%20tomatoes%20in%20their%20store%20room%2C%20but%20no%20luck%20so%20far%3A%20the%20sourness%20never%20varies!%20The%20progeny%20of%20Gulati%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%2C%20thanks%20to%20COVID%2C%20developed%20a%20brand%20called%20Yours%20Truly%20Butter%20Chicken%20with%20seven%20variants%20of%20the%20same%20theme!%20Yes%2C%20that%20is%20how%20fanatical%20we%20are%20about%20our%20national%20dish%2C%20hereabouts.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20epicures%20have%20attempted%20to%20discover%20the%20secret%20behind%20the%20dish%E2%80%99s%20exquisite%20taste%2C%20some%20say%20it%20lies%20in%20the%20cream%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20specially%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F345649%2Fhistory-of-parsi-dairy-farm-mumbai-nariman-ardeshir-legacy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20dairy%20farm%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ashram%2C%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20Delhi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Aslam%20Butter%20Chicken%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Delhi%20touts%20its%20recipe%20of%20butter%20chicken%20as%20a%20simple%20one%2C%20Aslam%20Butter%20Chicken%2C%20which%20has%20been%20doling%20out%20the%20delicacy%20for%2025%20years%20now%2C%20strays%20away%20from%20this%20levity.%20Secret%20%3Cem%3Emasalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20roasted%20and%20charcoal-grilled%20chicken%2C%20and%20of%20course%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20butter%20go%20into%20the%20recipe%20at%20Aslam%E2%80%99s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwgycX7iscXg%3Fsi%3DdMq2Yp_isBLuq2OB%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recipe%20is%20a%20well-guarded%20secret%20that%20is%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations%20of%20the%20family.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20Aslam%20learnt%20it%20from%20his%20father%20and%20grandfather%3B%20till%20date%2C%20this%20consistency%20reflects%20in%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%