%20of%20the%20duo%20behind%20Buddy%20Up%20Network%20%E2%80%94%20a%20friendship%20app%20for%20individuals%20with%20disabilities.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20wish%20for%20every%20disabled%20person%20to%20find%20%E2%80%94%20a%20friendship%20where%20they%20can%20be%20themselves%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gopika%20shares.%20And%20Moneisha%20agrees.%20The%20app%2C%20they%20explain%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20those%20who%20are%20inclined%20to%20more%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F120681%2Finclov-app-differently-abled-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeclectic%20patterns%20of%20friendship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20who%20veer%20away%20from%20contemporary%20definitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Vir%20and%20Mihaan%20for%20instance.%20They%20enjoy%20starkly%20different%20hobbies.%20While%20Vir%20loves%20a%20good%20puzzle%20and%20spends%20his%20time%20cycling%2C%20swimming%2C%20running%20and%20baking%2C%20Mihaan%20is%20a%20music%20aficionado.%20I%20wonder%20where%20they%20find%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20humour%20is%20the%20adhesive%20in%20this%20friendship!%20But%20their%20symbiotic%20relationship%20isn%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20cackling%20at%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20jokes.%20It%20also%20extends%20to%20appreciating%20the%20other%E2%80%99s%20talents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVir%20makes%20aircraft%20and%20windmill%20models%20with%20LEGO%20blocks%20and%20makes%20them%20move%20by%20attaching%20a%20machine%20to%20them.%20It%E2%80%99s%20so%20cool!%E2%80%9D%20Mihaan%20is%20in%20awe%20and%20makes%20it%20a%20point%20to%20express%20it%20every%20chance%20he%20gets.%20Vir%20appreciates%20this.%20Sharing%20his%20uncomfortable%20history%20of%20making%20new%20friends%2C