0class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Buddy%20Up%20Network%20app%20is%20available%20for%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%20of%20all%20age%20groups%20and%20is%20designed%20to%20help%20users%20connect%20with%20friends%20who%20share%20similar%20passions.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20app%20is%20available%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English%20and%20allows%20users%20to%20search%20for%20friends%20based%20on%20age%2C%20location%2C%20interests%2C%20disability%2C%20and%20gender.%20It%20can%20help%20find%20friends%20for%20people%20with%20all%20disabilities%20and%20of%20all%20ages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20stepping%20away%20from%20the%20demographics%2C%20Moneisha%20says%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20this%20project%20is%20the%20idea%20of%20finding%20a%20friend.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20disability%20community%2C%20when%20kids%20are%20young%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296192%2Fshraddha-soparkar-provides-free-therapy-to-children-with-disabilities-madhuram-charitable-trust%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20focus%20is%20on%20therapy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20school.%20When%20they%20are%20older%2C%20it%20becomes%20about%20jobs.%20No%20one%20focuses%20on%20friendship.%20But%20we%20believe%20that%20friendship%20is%20as%20important%20as%20any%20of%20these%20other%20things.%20We%20saw%20how%20powerful%20a%20connection%20like%20this%20has%20been%20for%20our%20boys.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMihaan%E2%80%99s%20words%20ring%20true%2C%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20should%20have%20a%20friend.%E2%80%9D%20On%20second%20thoughts%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20friend%20like%20Vir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Pictures%20source%3A%20Moneisha%20Gandhi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733207533000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-m